== Births == * [[Antei]] 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1227]] {{ill|June 29|ja|6月29日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Hojo Tokiyori|ja|北条時頼|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the 5th shikken of the Kamakura shogunate (died [[1263]]). * {{ill|Kansei|ja|寛政|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 5th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1793]] {{ill|June 22|ja|6月22日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Tokugawa Iekei|ja|徳川家慶|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the 12th shōgun of the Tokugawa shogunate (died [[1853]]).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 16th year (leap May) ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1588]] {{ill|July 7|ja|7月7日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Sasasa Narimasa|ja|佐々成政|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a military commander ({{ill|Busho (Rank)|ja|武将|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) (born [[1516]]). * [[Keichō]] 11th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1606]] {{ill|June 19|ja|6月19日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Sakakibara Yasumasa|ja|榊原康政|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a military commander and one of the Tokugawa Four Heavenly Kings (born [[1548]]). <“{{ill|Tokugawa Tsuneyoshi|ja|徳川綱教|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}” has a note stating “May 18” in another account.> == Commemorations == == See Also == {{Lunar Calendar See Also|5|13|5|15|4|14|6|5|0514}}
