{{afc comment|1=This article as with the other date articles is relatively limited in scope to Japan. Reviewing the translation of this is good and also adding content translated from Chinese and Korean wikipedias will also be good. Both wikipedias are also relatively centered around their own countries for their Lunisolar calendar dates[[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 00:16, 28 April 2025 (UTC)}} {{Globalize|article|Japan|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Chinese|1=五月十四|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Korean|1=음력 5월 14일|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Lunisolar May|qq=}} '''May 14''' is the 14th day of the month {{ill|May (Lunisolar)|ja|5月 (旧暦)|lt=May (Satsuki)|qq=}}, the 5th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=}} day is {{ill|Shakkō|ja|赤口|qq=}}.
== Events == * {{ill|Jōkyū|ja|承久|qq=}} 3rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} [[1221]] {{ill|June 5|ja|6月5日|qq=}}) – In the incident known as {{ill|Jōkyū no Ran|ja|承久の乱|qq=}}, the forces of the Kamakura shogunate, seeking to overthrow the regime, were assembled by {{ill|Go-Toba†Go-Toba_Tennō|ja|後鳥羽上皇|qq=}} along with approximately 1700 samurai from neighboring provinces. * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|qq=}} 10th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} [[1839]] {{ill|June 24|ja|6月24日|qq=}}) – In the event known as the {{ill|Bansha no Goku|ja|蛮社の獄|qq=}}, figures such as {{ill|Watanabe Kōzan|ja|渡辺崋山|qq=}} and {{ill|Takano Chōei|ja|高野長英|qq=}} were arrested. * {{ill|Genji|ja|元治|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} [[1864]] {{ill|June 17|ja|6月17日|qq=}}) – The Tokugawa shogunate established the Kobe Naval Training Center, appointing {{ill|Katsu Kaishū|ja|勝海舟|qq=}} as its head.
== Births == * [[Antei]] 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} [[1227]] {{ill|June 29|ja|6月29日|qq=}}) – {{ill|Hojo Tokiyori|ja|北条時頼|qq=}}, the 5th shikken of the Kamakura shogunate (died [[1263]]). * {{ill|Kansei|ja|寛政|qq=}} 5th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} [[1793]] {{ill|June 22|ja|6月22日|qq=}}) – {{ill|Tokugawa Iekei|ja|徳川家慶|qq=}}, the 12th shōgun of the Tokugawa shogunate (died [[1853]]).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|qq=}} 16th year (leap May) ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} [[1588]] {{ill|July 7|ja|7月7日|qq=}}) – {{ill|Sasasa Narimasa|ja|佐々成政|qq=}}, a military commander ({{ill|Busho (Rank)|ja|武将|qq=}}) (born [[1516]]). * [[Keichō]] 11th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} [[1606]] {{ill|June 19|ja|6月19日|qq=}}) – {{ill|Sakakibara Yasumasa|ja|榊原康政|qq=}}, a military commander and one of the Tokugawa Four Heavenly Kings (born [[1548]]). <“{{ill|Tokugawa Tsuneyoshi|ja|徳川綱教|qq=}}” has a note stating “May 18” in another account.> == Commemorations == == See Also == {{Lunar Calendar See Also|5|13|5|15|4|14|6|5|0514|qq=}}
