== Events == * {{ill|Jōkyū|ja|承久|qq=|qq=draft}} 3rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft}} [[1221]] {{ill|June 5|ja|6月5日|qq=|qq=draft}}) – In the incident known as {{ill|Jōkyū no Ran|ja|承久の乱|qq=|qq=draft}}, the forces of the Kamakura shogunate, seeking to overthrow the regime, were assembled by {{ill|Go-Toba†Go-Toba_Tennō|ja|後鳥羽上皇|qq=|qq=draft}} along with approximately 1700 samurai from neighboring provinces. * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|qq=|qq=draft}} 10th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft}} [[1839]] {{ill|June 24|ja|6月24日|qq=|qq=draft}}) – In the event known as the {{ill|Bansha no Goku|ja|蛮社の獄|qq=|qq=draft}}, figures such as {{ill|Watanabe Kōzan|ja|渡辺崋山|qq=|qq=draft}} and {{ill|Takano Chōei|ja|高野長英|qq=|qq=draft}} were arrested. * {{ill|Genji|ja|元治|qq=|qq=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft}} [[1864]] {{ill|June 17|ja|6月17日|qq=|qq=draft}}) – The Tokugawa shogunate established the Kobe Naval Training Center, appointing {{ill|Katsu Kaishū|ja|勝海舟|qq=|qq=draft}} as its head.
== Births == * [[Antei]] 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft}} [[1227]] {{ill|June 29|ja|6月29日|qq=|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Hojo Tokiyori|ja|北条時頼|qq=|qq=draft}}, the 5th shikken of the Kamakura shogunate (died [[1263]]). * {{ill|Kansei|ja|寛政|qq=|qq=draft}} 5th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft}} [[1793]] {{ill|June 22|ja|6月22日|qq=|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Tokugawa Iekei|ja|徳川家慶|qq=|qq=draft}}, the 12th shōgun of the Tokugawa shogunate (died [[1853]]).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|qq=|qq=draft}} 16th year (leap May) ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft}} [[1588]] {{ill|July 7|ja|7月7日|qq=|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Sasasa Narimasa|ja|佐々成政|qq=|qq=draft}}, a military commander ({{ill|Busho (Rank)|ja|武将|qq=|qq=draft}}) (born [[1516]]). * [[Keichō]] 11th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft}} [[1606]] {{ill|June 19|ja|6月19日|qq=|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Sakakibara Yasumasa|ja|榊原康政|qq=|qq=draft}}, a military commander and one of the Tokugawa Four Heavenly Kings (born [[1548]]). <“{{ill|Tokugawa Tsuneyoshi|ja|徳川綱教|qq=|qq=draft}}” has a note stating “May 18” in another account.> == Commemorations == == See Also == {{Lunar Calendar See Also|5|13|5|15|4|14|6|5|0514|qq=}}
