== Events == * {{ill|Jōkyū|ja|承久|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jōkyū|qq=}} 3rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[1221]] {{ill|June 5|ja|6月5日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 5|qq=}}) – In the incident known as {{ill|Jōkyū no Ran|ja|承久の乱|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jōkyū no Ran|qq=}}, the forces of the Kamakura shogunate, seeking to overthrow the regime, were assembled by {{ill|Go-Toba†Go-Toba_Tennō|ja|後鳥羽上皇|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Go-Toba†Go-Toba_Tennō|qq=}} along with approximately 1700 samurai from neighboring provinces. * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenpō|qq=}} 10th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1839]] {{ill|June 24|ja|6月24日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 24|qq=}}) – In the event known as the {{ill|Bansha no Goku|ja|蛮社の獄|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bansha no Goku|qq=}}, figures such as {{ill|Watanabe Kōzan|ja|渡辺崋山|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Watanabe Kōzan|qq=}} and {{ill|Takano Chōei|ja|高野長英|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Takano Chōei|qq=}} were arrested. * {{ill|Genji|ja|元治|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Genji|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1864]] {{ill|June 17|ja|6月17日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 17|qq=}}) – The Tokugawa shogunate established the Kobe Naval Training Center, appointing {{ill|Katsu Kaishū|ja|勝海舟|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Katsu Kaishū|qq=}} as its head.
