== Events == * [[:en:Jōkyū|Jōkyū]] 3rd year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1221|1221]] [[:en:June 5|June 5]]) – In the incident known as [[:en:Jōkyū War|Jōkyū no Ran]], the forces of the Kamakura shogunate, seeking to overthrow the regime, were assembled by {{ill|Go-Toba†Go-Toba_Tennō|ja|後鳥羽上皇|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Go-Toba†Go-Toba_Tennō|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 後鳥羽天皇}} along with approximately 1700 samurai from neighboring provinces. * [[:en:Tenpō|Tenpō]] 10th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1839|1839]] [[:en:June 24|June 24]]) – In the event known as the [[:en:Bansha no goku|Bansha no Goku]], figures such as [[:en:Watanabe Kazan|Watanabe Kōzan]] and [[:en:Takano Chōei|Takano Chōei]] were arrested. * [[:en:Genji era|Genji]] 1st year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1864|1864]] [[:en:June 17|June 17]]) – The Tokugawa shogunate established the Kobe Naval Training Center, appointing [[:en:Katsu Kaishū|Katsu Kaishū]] as its head.
== Births == * [[Antei]] 1st year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1227|1227]] [[:en:June 29|June 29]]) – [[:en:Hōjō Tokiyori|Hojo Tokiyori]], the 5th shikken of the Kamakura shogunate (died [[:en:1263|1263]]). * [[:en:Kansei|Kansei]] 5th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1793|1793]] [[:en:June 22|June 22]]) – [[:en:Tokugawa Ieyoshi|Tokugawa Iekei]], the 12th shōgun of the Tokugawa shogunate (died [[:en:1853|1853]]).
== Deaths == * [[:en:Tenshō (Momoyama period)|Tenshō Era]] 16th year (leap May) ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1588|1588]] [[:en:July 7|July 7]]) – [[:en:Sassa Narimasa|Sasasa Narimasa]], a military commander ({{ill|Busho (Rank)|ja|武将|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Busho (Rank)|qq=}}) (born [[:en:1516|1516]]). * [[Keichō]] 11th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1606|1606]] [[:en:June 19|June 19]]) – [[:en:Sakakibara Yasumasa|Sakakibara Yasumasa]], a military commander and one of the Tokugawa Four Heavenly Kings (born [[:en:1548|1548]]). <“{{ill|Tokugawa Tsuneyoshi|ja|徳川綱教|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tokugawa Tsuneyoshi|qq=}}” has a note stating “May 18” in another account.> == Commemorations == == See Also == {{Lunar Calendar See Also|5|13|5|15|4|14|6|5|0514|qq=}}
